channel.title: The Chanel 3102 | CH3102
channel.description: Chanel was founded in 1909 by Gabrielle ‘Coco’ Chanel. Coco Chanel learnt how to be a seamstress whilst growing up in an orphanage. After leaving, she eventually started her own milliners shop, designing hats for wealthy ladies. Soon, she started designing clothing, first focusing on comfortable designs for leisure, then eventually moving to practical clothing [...]
